            <title>[LU-16359] RHEL find-provides fails on newer kernels</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-16359</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;RHEL find-provides fails on newer kernels&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This creates rpms that cannot be installed with &apos;yum&apos; or &apos;dnf&apos;.&lt;br/&gt;
As a workaround rpm can still be used with --nodeps.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
